Package de.rwth.i2.attestor.grammar.materialization.indexedGrammar

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    IndexedGrammarResponseApplier
    Capable of handling MaterializationAndRuleResponse in addition to all GrammarResponses handled by DefaultGrammarResponseApplier
    IndexedMaterializationRuleManager
    Computes and caches the rules for resolving a given violation point for IndexedNonterminals in addition to all Nonterminals handled by DefaultMaterializationRuleManager.
    IndexedRuleAdapter  
    IndexMaterializationStrategy
    Responsible for applying the materialization rules to the indices of the nonterminals in the graph.
